  "description": "Consolidated recommendations + preference analytics. Merges the former Recs/Engine, Recs/Content Preferences, and Player/Preference Resolution dashboards (2026-06-03). Rows: Recommendations (rec_* CTR/click/watch, pin signal), Audience Splits (player/language/dub-sub from watch_episodes_total), Translation Rankings (translation_selections_total), Resolution (preference_resolution_total tiers), Overrides (combo_override_total / combo_resolve_total). The dead preference_fallback_total panels were dropped (no producer in code \u2014 see ISS-026's sibling note).",
